{"text_id":105057,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," explore"," the"," survival"," of"," millimeter"," to"," centimeter","-","sized"," grains"," in"," pro","top","lan","etary"," disks","."," The"," problem"," we"," aim"," to"," solve"," pertains"," to"," the"," seemingly"," contradictory"," observations"," of"," grain"," growth"," and"," limited"," grain"," retention"," in"," such"," disks","."," While"," pro","top","lan","etary"," disks"," are"," known"," to"," be"," the"," birth","places"," of"," planets",","," it"," remains"," unclear"," how"," the"," growth"," of"," dust"," grains"," from"," micron"," to"," millimeter"," sizes"," occurs"," and"," how"," these"," grains"," are"," ultimately"," retained"," or"," lost"," from"," their"," natal"," disks","."," Our"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," is"," to"," gain"," a"," better"," understanding"," of"," the"," formation"," of"," planets"," and"," planetary"," systems",","," which"," is"," vital"," in"," understanding"," our"," own"," solar"," system"," and"," its"," history","."," To"," achieve"," this",","," we"," utilize"," a"," high","-","resolution"," numerical"," model"," to"," simulate"," dust"," dynamics"," in"," pro","top","lan","etary"," disks","."," This"," allows"," us"," to"," investigate"," the"," growth"," and"," survival"," of"," grain"," populations"," of"," different"," sizes"," under"," varying"," conditions","."," We"," find"," that"," while"," larger"," grains"," are"," more"," likely"," to"," be"," retained",","," the"," survival"," of"," smaller"," grains"," is"," imperative"," for"," the"," growth"," of"," larger"," grains","."," Our"," key"," finding"," is"," that"," turbulence"," plays"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," both"," the"," evolution"," of"," dust"," and"," the"," retention"," of"," grains","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," a"," combination"," of"," numerical"," simulations",","," analytical"," calculations",","," and"," comparison"," with"," observational"," data","."," Our"," results"," have"," significant"," implications"," for"," the"," formation"," and"," evolution"," of"," planets"," and"," contribute"," to"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," processes"," that"," shape"," pro","top","lan","etary"," disks","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}